129
00:08:47,033 --> 00:08:48,988
Os anticorpos
desativarão o Kusari.

130
00:08:48,989 --> 00:08:51,102
<i>Negativo.
Estamos saindo.</i>

131
00:08:53,105 --> 00:08:54,505
Dr. Maraj?

132
00:08:55,775 --> 00:08:58,975
